stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> GeneratedSql
    GeneratedSql --> Validating
    Validating --> Executable: pass
    Validating --> CorrectableError: syntax / column / dialect
    Validating --> HardReject: readonly / ACL / parse rejected
    CorrectableError --> CorrectionAttempt: attempts below max
    CorrectionAttempt --> Validating
    CorrectableError --> HardReject: attempts exhausted
    Executable --> ExecuteSql
    ExecuteSql --> GroundedAnswer: rows returned
    ExecuteSql --> EmptyResultAnswer: rows = 0
    HardReject --> RefusalAnswer
    GroundedAnswer --> Replay
    EmptyResultAnswer --> Replay
    RefusalAnswer --> Replay
